==Finnish==
{{Finnish index|ti}}

===Etymology===
Derived from ''[[tie]]'' 'road, way'. The verb apparently meant originally 'to know the way'.

===Verb===
'''tietää'''

# to [[know]]
# to [[signify]], [[mean]], [[presage]], [[spell]]

